        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-21 18:30:01.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWhat is the impact of not having this in?  I'm guessing from the defect that the UI won't work with the latest OXM schema without the change.  Just trying to determine if this needs to be in Casablanca.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "d40d508975ce4f07d74854a5bfdbc0ea34ece64b",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 651,
          "name": "Francis Paquette",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "Francis.Paquette@amdocs.com",
          "username": "fpaquett"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-21 18:34:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: -Code-Review\n\nSteve, I talked about this with Jimmy on Wednesday and he agreed to making the change.\n\nNot having this in means that data-router won't be able to read oxm v14.\n\nThis would also mean that sparky configuration would need to be rev down to v13.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
